<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.5.1">
<l>aṭṭuk kuvicōṟ ṟuparup patamum</l>
<l rend="indent">tayirvā viyumney yaḷaṟu maṭaṅkap</l>
<l>poṭṭat tuṟṟi mārippakai puṇartta</l>
<l rend="indent">porumā kaṭalvaṇ ṇaṉpoṟut tamalai</l>
<l>vaṭṭat taṭaṅkaṇ maṭamāṉ kaṉṟiṉai</l>
<l rend="indent">valaivāyp paṟṟikkoṇ ṭukuṟa makaḷir</l>
<l>koṭṭait talaippāl koṭuttu vaḷarkkum</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvart taṉameṉ ṉumkoṟṟak kuṭaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain that was borne by the one with a complexion [like] the great, churning sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">who brought about the enmity of the rain clouds</l>
<l rend="indent">after [he] swiftly and thoroughly ate</l>
<l rend="indent"> the heaping mountain of cooked rice,</l>
<l rend="indent">river of curd, and bog of ghee,</l>
<l>called Govardhana,</l>
<l rend="Indent">where little girls catch simple, round,</l>
<l rend="indent">wide eyed fawn in nets and take [them]</l>
<l rend="indent">to give [them] milk on the end of a cloth knot</l>
<l rend="indent">[to suckle] and raise [them],</l>
<l>is [his] victory umbrella.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
